Array kya hota hai?

Array multiple values ko ek hi variable mein store karta hai. Iske elements ko index (0, 1, 2...) se access kiya jata hai.

Object kya hota hai?

Object data ko key-value pairs ki form mein store karta hai. Iski values ko key (property name) se access kiya jata hai.

Array mein data index ke through access hota hai, jabke object mein data key (property name) ke through access hota hai.